{"tid":1536601,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"8/9果日，我地除左要支持香港民主法之外，仲要表明支持美國追回清朝債券","createTime":"2019-09-03T16:35:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T07:28:32.000Z","uid":241904,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"cd2049b15fbe73b809fa5fd0fe33e5aabfa6c848","tid":1536601,"uid":241904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:35:42.000Z","msg":"Donald trump 之前已經放晒水，叫中國償還清朝債券，言下之意係一係叫中國還番10萬億美金既國債，一係就承認係國際法上對香港係非法管治<br />\n<br />\n9/9就係美國國會復會既日子，香港人都打算係8/9向美國表達我地對於香港民主法既支持，不如我地同時都表達支持美國追討清朝債券？等美國人知道我地同樣有決心要對抗日漸強大而獨裁既中國，我地係希望free Hong Kong既同時都希望make American great again<br />\n<br />\n希望有文宣可以整下相關既野同埋巴絲可以講下有冇其他意見<br />\n<br />\n最後，我係另一個po留過想關既idea, 都有唔少人讚成<br />\n希望咁多位推過既可以再幫手推一下，因為我仲未甩到p呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed3f2a2dd29b2c415c8f2731d1925c34a4e9b9d6","tid":1536601,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:37:59.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06a4110438a587c108baaf92890b90c19effb64c","tid":1536601,"uid":171788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:47:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zdS50W9Aq_Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzdS50W9Aq_Y&d=KYuNOZm%2F4ip93LesI4%2B6vkzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=a1553095\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zdS50W9Aq_Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zdS50W9Aq_Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzdS50W9Aq_Y&d=KYuNOZm%2F4ip93LesI4%2B6vkzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=a1553095\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zdS50W9Aq_Y</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pCEXWLt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpCEXWLt.jpg&h=9e5ff431&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nThe one and only one chance to end game !"},{"pid":"dcf62c21ae4fdf47336f361996e7da7ce9038541","tid":1536601,"uid":121112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:48:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">而家既香港管治檯，法律上係屬於英國，其次係最大債權國美國，第三就係手持南京條約既台灣。中國對香港既管治，係國際法上，係非法管治</span>"},{"pid":"41a789b772fdb43bad55f52912f1b6953f8667f5","tid":1536601,"uid":202876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:32:41.000Z","msg":"自古以來啊嗱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd7abbdc007ea844419a57ae7394e2d57d2ec06a","tid":1536601,"uid":241904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T23:25:18.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"34d8819d87dac95bb18e494a